<div class='equipment'>
  <p>
    <span class='removal_link'><%= remove_link( form ) %></span>
    <span class='title'>Laptop</span>
    <%= form.hidden_field :equipment_type, :value => 'laptop' %>
    <%= form.hidden_field :first, :value => true if form.object.first? %>
  </p>
  <p>
    In order for us to be able to use your computer it will need to meet certain requirements. It must be running at least Microsoft Windows XP, have a processor type
    of a Pentium IV or greater, have a processor speed of 900Mhz or greater, have at least 512 megabytes of memory, and have at least 20 Gigabytes of space available on the internal hard drive.
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :meets_requirements, 'Does your computer meet the above requirements?: ' %><%= form.select :meets_requirements, ['Yes','No'], :prompt => '- Select -' %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :brand, 'Brand: ' %><%= form.text_field :brand, :size => 20 %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :operating_system, 'Operating System: ' %><%= form.select :operating_system, ['Windows XP','Windows Vista','Windows 7','Windows 8','Windows 8.1','Windows 10','Window 11'], :prompt => '- Select -' %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :parallel_port, 'Parallel Port Type: ' %><%= form.select :parallel_port, ['Built In','PCMCIA Card','Express Card','None'], :prompt => '- Select -' %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :quizmachine_version, 'Quizmachine Version: ' %><%= form.text_field :quizmachine_version, :size => 30 %><br/>
    To find your quizmachine version, start quizmachine, click Setup/Exit, click Yes. Version is listed near the top left of the screen.
  </p>
  <p>
    Does your computer require a username and password? If so please let us know whet they are, reset them to something that can be used for the event, or remove them temporarily for the event.
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :username, 'Username: ' %><%= form.text_field :username, :size => 30 %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :password, 'Password: ' %><%= form.text_field :password, :size => 30 %>
  </p>
</div>